divs: Sighting DetailsI was at the Crow's Nest at the Santa Cruz marina with a friend having diner. I was taking pictures of the sunset, the view and the passing boats. I did not see the objects with my own eyes but did notice them later when I was reviewing the photos. The images where taken using and iPhone 4 and at no more than 50% zoom It is important to note that I feel the objects could be reflections in the glass but can't be certain of this. I leave it up to you to investigate. I hope it helps.
